data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis nestled within the beautiful, gated neighborhood of Forest Creek. This thoughtful floor plan features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a DEN or OFFICE that provides versatility and a spacious kitchen that boasts a large pantry and walk-through laundry room, making daily tasks a breeze. This home features upgrades including: plantation shutters, tray ceiling, beautiful trim details, chandeliers and light fixtures. The home has a gorgeous coastal vibe and can be purchased fully furnished or unfurnished. From the open living room you step onto the extended lanai overlooking the tranquil pond, providing a peaceful and private outdoor space. Enjoy the community's amenities, including pool and spa, fitness center, playground, dog park, scenic walking trails and community dock that overlooks the 18 acre lake where you can fish, kayak and canoe, relish in the serene ambiance of this thoughtfully landscaped oasis. Experience luxury and comfort at its finest – schedule a showing today and seize the opportunity to make this exceptional residence your own.
